%h1 Topics

- @topics.each do |topic| 
  = link_to subtopics_path+"?topic_id=#{topic.id}" do
    .topic{class: "#{'finished' if current_user.is_finished_with?(topic)}"}
      = topic.name
  %br
  %br
  %br
  %br
  - if current_user && current_user.admin?
    = link_to('edit', edit_topic_path(topic))
    = link_to('delete', topic_path(topic), method: :delete, confirm: 'Are you sure you want to delete this topic?')